---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="山の和 | News | Takuya Asano"
  description="Information for the spring gathering '山の和' at Jeenya in Akiu, Sendai."
  ogImage="https://asanotakuya.com/images/yamanowa-flyer.jpg"
  ogUrl="https://asanotakuya.com/news/yamanowa"
  ogType="article"
>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container header-inner">
      <a href="/" class="site-title">Takuya Asano</a>
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="/works">Works</a>
        <a href="/news">News</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <article class="news-post">
        <a href="/news" class="back-link fade-in">← Back to News</a>

        <header class="news-post-header fade-in">
          <p class="news-date">2026.04.11</p>
          <h1 class="news-post-title">山の和</h1>
        </header>

        <div class="news-post-content fade-in">
          <p class="news-intro-en">
            A live performance took place in Akiu, Sendai on April 11, 2026.
          </p>

          <div class="news-body">
            <p>日程：2026年4月11日（土）</p>
            <p>時間：11:00 – 16:00</p>
            <p>会場：Jeenya（仙台市秋保町馬場字辺田86）</p>

            <br />

            <p>
              出店：<br />
              ミュゲ花屋／ペンギン文庫／bau leather／Roebling<br />
              ダモコーヒーハウス／cookie girl／本沢三丁目パン工房／Jeenya ほか
            </p>

            <br />

            <p>演奏：浅野託矢</p>
            <p>開始：14:00頃（約30–40分）</p>

            <br />

            <p>
              主催：
              <a
                href="https://www.instagram.com/jeenya.7/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
              >
                @jeenya.7
              </a>
            </p>

            <br />

            <p>
              備考：<br />
              雨天時は4月12日（日）へ順延<br />
              両日雨天の場合は内容を変更して開催
            </p>

            <br />

            <p>
              ※内容は変更となる場合があります。<br />
              最新情報は主催者の案内をご確認ください。
            </p>
          </div>

          <figure class="news-flyer">
            <img src="/images/yamanowa-flyer.jpg" alt="山の和 フライヤー" />
          </figure>

          <p class="news-note-en">
            Please refer to the organizer's announcement for the latest information.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>

  <script is:inline>
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry) => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add("is-visible");
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.12 });

    document.querySelectorAll(".fade-in").forEach((el) => observer.observe(el));
  </script>
  <style>
    .news-post {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .back-link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    }

    .back-link:hover {
      opacity: 0.65;
    }

    .news-post-header {
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .news-date {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    .news-post-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", "Noto Serif JP", serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      line-height: 1.12;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }

    .news-post-content p {
      margin: 0 0 20px;
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", "Noto Serif JP", serif;
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      line-height: 1.72;
      letter-spacing: 0.008em;
      color: #333333;
    }

    .news-intro-en {
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    .news-body p {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", "Noto Serif JP", serif;
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
      letter-spacing: 0.008em;
      color: #333333;
    }

    .news-body a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-underline-offset: 0.12em;
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    }

    .news-body a:hover {
      opacity: 0.65;
    }

    .news-flyer {
      margin: 48px 0 40px;
      max-width: 60%;
    }

    .news-flyer img {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      opacity: 0.92;
    }

    .news-note-en {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .back-link {
        margin-bottom: 32px;
        font-size: 0.92rem;
      }

      .news-post-header {
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .news-flyer {
        max-width: 100%;
        margin: 36px 0 28px;
      }

      .news-post-content p,
      .news-body p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.68;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
